 P(2X \le Y) = P(\{(x,y) \in \mathbb{R^2} \mid 2x \le y \}) = \int_{\{(x,y) \in \mathbb{R}^2 \mid 2x \le y \}} f_{X,Y}(x,y) \, \mathrm{d} A 
